SELECT campaignName, campaignSlug, customerName, customerEmail, customerPhone, 1, 0, id, NOW(), NOW() 
FROM purchases 
WHERE customerEmail = 'guilhermeram@gmail.com' 
ORDER BY id DESC 
LIMIT 1;
